rComments: If you want a class where you can get an A or even higher by not attending a single lecture, this is the course for you. Do the readings and supplement your knowledge with his lecture slides and you're good. his exams have MCQs, short answer, and longer-short answer questions on them. As a prof, he's super caring and very reachable outside of class
His lectures are based on the notes he posts before class. He is accessible and easy to talk to. Really helpful.
